Package it.unipv.ingsfw.JavaBeats.model.profile

Class JBProfile

java.lang.Object
it.unipv.ingsfw.JavaBeats.model.profile.JBProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
IJBResearchable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Artist, User
public abstract class JBProfile extends Object implements IJBResearchable
Abstract class representing a generic JavaBeats profile. Contains attributes and methods common both to User and Artist.
